        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Pin-Joints in the graphic-area</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> &#160;</text><image src="MD-Dowel-Symbol.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:7pt; vertical-align:sub; color:#0000ff;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-style:italic;"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">symbol for a </text><text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> that is fixed to the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-BasePart" styleclass="Element">Base-Part</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption"> &#160;</text><image src="MD-PointandPinJoint-Symbol.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> the </text><text styleclass="Body Text">outer circle is the </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">symbol for a </text><text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that moves relative to the </text><text styleclass="Element">Base-Part.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">The <text styleclass="Body Text">inner circle</text> is the <text styleclass="Interface">symbol</text> for the <text styleclass="Element">Points</text> that become coincident when you do <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Pin-Joint</text>.</para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">&lt;&lt;&lt; <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> between a <text styleclass="Element">Part</text> and the <text styleclass="Element">Base-Part.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">&lt;&lt;&lt; <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> &#160;between two(2) added <text styleclass="Element">Parts.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
